use std.io_runtime

# simple-payment: Credit and payment access interface library
# MDSOC+ architecture — SFM Trusted module
#
# Capsules:
#   gateway/  — payment connector abstraction (authorize/capture/charge/refund/void/tokenize)
#   vault/    — tokenized card storage (never stores raw PAN/CVV)
#   card/     — card types, validation, HW reader trait
#   agent/    — LLM agent tool + CLI payment interface
#   sfm/      — SFM manifest + packaging (Trusted security level)
